The paper discusses a cross-layer scheme for collaborative beamforming in wireless networks, which involves techniques from information theory (cs.IT), networking (cs.NI), signal processing (cs.SY), multimedia (cs.MM), and performance analysis (cs.PF). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories that this paper belongs to, ordered from most to least likely.
